{"tid":1476101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解黑警係裡面打手足冇人講？","createTime":"2019-08-15T16:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T17:15:39.000Z","uid":273495,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"02abe68d3bd8c19efc45911b77ca5f4c1ff4e028","tid":1476101,"uid":273495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:44:33.000Z","msg":"大家都聽過有30幾位手足比黑警係裡面打<br />\n之前40幾個暴動既都有比人放係一個熱既停車場到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尼單野唔可以睇小</span></span><br />\n可唔可以煲大佢？而家係用緊私刑啊DLLM<br />\n可況有d真係唔過比人拉<br />\n如果成拉個基金或者律師團之類<br />\n再搵願意出聲既受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去告警察有冇可能？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔識法律，有冇法律jj可以答我點幫佢地攞翻個公道？<br />\n可唔可以眾籌幫佢地打官司告黑警？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比單野僅限於只係得文字既資料！"},{"pid":"dba3c1e35024b927c6643cc36bbd0f9fbaec5f3c","tid":1476101,"uid":138357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n手足唔係condom!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5c058b18f9c380a83240a52ec5485c4d24191e","tid":1476101,"uid":43493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"報俾鏗鏘集<br />\nfacebook can nbox佢地<br />\n認真"},{"pid":"59755d94f23a4d5dff47b7c3b8cc67bcde8ecf59","tid":1476101,"uid":141419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:47:08.000Z","msg":"題外問，除左電話有冇咩有攝錄功能？<br />\n有我哋買定批俾香港人用<br />\n最好唔好大舊<br />\n有冇巴打有意見？"},{"pid":"40ad5220ee9bb903a68befb9d90f4525a65a3c2b","tid":1476101,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"大大力推"},{"pid":"3915981fc335926e03cfe946734f72c8d15b517e","tid":1476101,"uid":273495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:47:38.000Z","msg":"係咁打錯字 自己都識個朋友住黃大仙<br />\n翻個屋企比人拉 照告<br />\n我相信受害者好多 佢地冇做錯架<img sr